1.2 - AML 2002.03.10
	* changed gcc compile flag to -O (was -O2) to avoid compilation errors
	* fixed libtool configuration, so that libraries
	  don't complain about not being in /usr/local/lib
	
1.1 - AML 2001.09.30
	* changed build structure to a gnu style setup so as
	  to allow clean compilation on OS X
	* removed dclz compression method due to licensing, 
	  and lack of use
	* renamed compress to z_compress (needed for OS X)
	* renamed uncompress to z_uncompress (needed for OS X)
	* removed rts_wdat function in rts_cmd
	  -unused function, and screws up OS X compilation due to cfree call
	* removed a large number of unused files
	* removed values.h from utils/get_axial_lor.c
	* removed malloc.h includes 
	* changed references to -D__alpha to -DLITTLE_ENDIAN
	* changed references to -D__sun to -DBIG_ENDIAN

